General Information

Swisse Rosewater Hydrating Mist Toner is a daily calming mist infused with a blend of botanical extracts to soften the skin and deliver a dose of hydration. Formulated with Aloe Vera and Organic Rose Hip Extract, it helps to soothe, balance and nourish the skin, leaving skin feeling revitalised and refreshed.

Warnings

Natural fragrance may contain allergens from essential oils. Test prior to use. In the unlikely event of a negative reaction, consult your medical practitioner.

Ingredients

Water (Aqua) Polysorbate 20 Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Juice Rosa Damascena (Rose) Flower Oil Rosa Damascena (Rose) Flower Extract Rosa Canina (Rose Hip) Fruit Extract Glycerin (Plant Derived) Carrageenan Sodium Citrate Citric Acid Fragrance* Dehydroacetic Acid Benzyl Alcohol

Directions

Directions: Shake well before use. Close eyes and spray from distance. Apply under or over makeup as required to face and neck.
